{"tid":1549530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左美國國歌，大家要認識埋呢首God bless the USA","createTime":"2019-09-07T10:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T14:09:52.000Z","uid":30743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a89b9af7d070b8cdd2ed443a5606b754edf9ff","tid":1549530,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yH61hFsma24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyH61hFsma24&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=301d325c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yH61hFsma24</a><br />\n<br />\n係美國最hit愛國歌曲，大家要識，咁先引起到美國關注<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌有幾把炮！？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e5JmaUU4O_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe5JmaUU4O_g&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=1527ac8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e5JmaUU4O_g</a><br />\n<br />\n連Trump Trump喺就職典禮都要唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec2dcfad8e43e59a435e5337c8ba48df0c1f7d4","tid":1549530,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"&quot;God Bless The USA&quot;<br />\n<br />\nIf tomorrow all the things were gone I'd worked for all my life<br />\nAnd I had to start again with just my children and my wife<br />\nI'd thank my lucky stars to be livin' here today<br />\n'Cause the flag still stands for freedom and they can't take that away<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And I'm proud to be an American where at least I know I'm free<br />\nAnd <strong>I won't forget the men who died, who gave that right to me</strong><br />\nAnd I'd gladly stand up next to you and defend her still today<br />\n'Cause there ain't no doubt I love this land<br />\nGod bless the USA</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d825ff78985cf15445c006969bad4784e4e